text: Project Catwalk is the Netherlands version of the reality show Project Runway. Season 1 shown in 2007 and was won by Django Steenbakker. The show lasted 2 more seasons, for a total of 3 seasons, before being canceled. ==External links== *Official website Netherlands Category:2007 Dutch television series debuts Category:2007 in fashion Category:Dutch fashion Category:2007 Dutch television series endings Category:Dutch reality television series
